getAirstreamCampaigns.t.sol
├── when the user has no campaigns
│  └── it should return an empty array
└── when the user have campaigns
    ├── when the user has a LD campaign
    │  └── it should return the correct campaign
    ├── when the user has a LL campaign
    │  └── it should return the correct campaign
    └── when the user has a both LD and LL campaigns
       └── it should return the correct campaigns